# Stride Adaptive — Environment Configuration
# ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ⚠  NO AI API KEYS should appear here. All AI credentials live server-side
#    in the serverless proxy (e.g. Vercel/Netlify environment variables).
#
# VITE_PROXY_TARGET  — local dev only. Points to your local serverless gateway.
#                      In production this is unused; /api routes are native.
VITE_PROXY_TARGET=http://localhost:3001